    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="一、准备工作"><a href="#一、准备工作" class="headerlink" title="一、准备工作"></a>一、准备工作</h2><p>手机需要先root，然后安装三个软件</p><p><strong>BusyBox</strong> 安装Linux的支撑组件</p><p><strong>Linux Deploy</strong> Linux的容器</p><p><strong>JuiceSSH</strong> SSH连接软件</p><p> <img src="https://s2.ax1x.com/2019/12/12/Q6txMD.md.jpg" alt="Q6txMD.md.jpg"></p><h3 id="安装效果如下"><a href="#安装效果如下" class="headerlink" title="安装效果如下"></a>安装效果如下</h3><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="https://s2.ax1x.com/2019/12/12/Q6wucV.md.png" alt="Q6wucV.md.png" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption">Q6wucV.md.png</div>            </figure><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="https://s2.ax1x.com/2019/12/12/Q6wp1P.png" alt="Q6wp1P.png" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption">Q6wp1P.png</div>            </figure><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="https://s2.ax1x.com/2019/12/12/Q6dsS0.png" alt="Q6dsS0.png" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption">Q6dsS0.png</div>            </figure><h2 id="二、配置Linux-Deploy"><a href="#二、配置Linux-Deploy" class="headerlink" title="二、配置Linux Deploy"></a>二、配置Linux Deploy</h2><p>接下来打开Linux Deploy，先点击右下角的按钮，进入到Linux的配置界面，我试过很多给版本，目前的这个版本是最稳定的，建议配置的和我一样</p><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="https://www.imageoss.com/images/2019/12/12/TIM20191212164137.png" alt="TIM20191212164137.png" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption">TIM20191212164137.png</div>            </figure><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="https://www.imageoss.com/images/2019/12/12/TIM20191212164129.jpg" alt="TIM20191212164129.jpg" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption">TIM20191212164129.jpg</div>            </figure><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="https://www.imageoss.com/images/2019/12/12/TIM20191212164134.png" alt="TIM20191212164134.png" title="">                </div>                <div class="image-caption">TIM20191212164134.png</div>            </figure><h2 id="三、安装Linux"><a href="#三、安装Linux" class="headerlink" title="三、安装Linux"></a>三、安装Linux</h2><p>完成这些配置后返回首页面，点击右上角的三个点，然后点击安装。<br>因为源配置的是国内的源，速度快的话几分钟就好了。<br>当出现&lt;&lt;&lt;deploy时，就是完成了</p><p>这时就点击启动，然后用SSH连接工具，连接到Linux了。</p>]]></content>
    
